因可能係船被認為不適合航海, 或因未能向該港口支付必要費用)<br />\n<br />\n- 拖左一段時間, 船東放棄左架船同船上烏克蘭船員, 最後困左響船上一年先至被釋放, 而船及貨物就被充公<br />\n<br />\n詳情可以睇英國衛報 Andrew Roth:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2020/aug/04/beirut-explosion-huge-blast-port-lebanon-capital?page=with%3Ablock-5f2abee68f0871f06ad992c5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2Flive%2F2020%2Faug%2F04%2Fbeirut-explosion-huge-blast-port-lebanon-capital%3Fpage%3Dwith%253Ablock-5f2abee68f0871f06ad992c5&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeamrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=b547845e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2020/aug/04/beirut-explosion-huge-blast-port-lebanon-capital?page=with%3Ablock-5f2abee68f0871f06ad992c5</a>"}]}